Column.name: PRIMARY_FLAG
Column.commentInRDBMS: Indicates whether this is the primary address for the person.

Column.name: STYLE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Address style - foreign key to FND_TERRITORIES.

Column.name: ADDRESS_LINE1
Column.commentInRDBMS: The first line of the address.

Column.name: ADDRESS_LINE2
Column.commentInRDBMS: The second line of the address.

Column.name: ADDRESS_LINE3
Column.commentInRDBMS: The third line of the address.

Column.name: ADDRESS_TYPE
Column.commentInRDBMS: Address type, for example, home, business, weekend.

Column.name: POSTAL_CODE
Column.commentInRDBMS: National code to identify addresses in a specific country.

Column.name: REGION_1
Column.commentInRDBMS: Primary region in which the address is located.

Column.name: REGION_2
Column.commentInRDBMS: Sub region of region 1 in which the address is located.

Column.name: REGION_3
Column.commentInRDBMS: Sub region of region 2 in which the address is located.

Column.name: TELEPHONE_NUMBER_2
Column.commentInRDBMS: Second telephone number for the address.

Column.name: TELEPHONE_NUMBER_3
Column.commentInRDBMS: Third telephone number for the address.

Column.name: OBJECT_VERSION_NUMBER
Column.commentInRDBMS: System-generated version of row. Increments by one with each update.
